  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "VistaLighthouse_Text_YoureTheLatestChallenger",
      "en_US": [
        "...\n",
        "...\r",
        "...So, you’re the latest challenger\n",
        "up against the Sunyshore Gym...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VistaLighthouse_Text_IWantThrillAgain",
      "en_US": [
        "All right, I’ve decided!\r",
        "If I find you to be weak, I’m going to\n",
        "challenge the Pokémon League.\r",
        "I’m all done with renovating the Gym,\n",
        "so I don’t need to be here.\r",
        "More than anything, I want to have\n",
        "battles that can thrill me again.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VistaLighthouse_Text_UnleashArsenalAtYou",
      "en_US": [
        "As the toughest Gym Leader in Sinnoh,\n",
        "I’m going to unleash everything in\f",
        "my arsenal on you.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VistaLighthouse_Text_PlayerLookedThroughBinoculars",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} took a look through\n",
        "the binoculars.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VistaLighthouse_Text_LighthouseRepresentsSafety",
      "en_US": [
        "The Vista Lighthouse represents\n",
        "safety and protection to us Sailors."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "VistaLighthouse_Text_GoingFarAwayOneDay",
      "en_US": [
        "I love how far away you can see with\n",
        "the binoculars.\r",
        "I’m going to go that far away with\n",
        "my Pokémon one day!"
      ]
    },
